let station = "环线检测"
let obj = {
    code, station, ...plc["小车数据"][i]
    , ...plc["焊接小车数据"][i],
    ...plc["电性能小车数据"][i],
    ...plc["小车张力数据"][i]
}
msg.payload = obj
return msg;
